<h2>5.4 Delete Work Type (Soft Delete)</h2>
<p><span class="badge badge-delete">DELETE</span> <code>/api/masters/work-type/:code</code></p>
<p><strong>Description:</strong> Soft-deletes a work type record by setting `n_deleted = 1`.</p>

<h3>Database Queries Executed:</h3>
<pre>UPDATE "Tbl_WorkType"
SET 
  "n_deleted" = 1, 
  "d_modified" = NOW(), 
  "c_modifier" = $1
WHERE "c_code" = $2;</pre>

